# CI checks for Python changes

Canonical instructions: [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md).

Before marking Python work complete, run from the repository root:

```bash
poetry run ruff check .
poetry run ruff format --check .
poetry run pyright .
poetry run pytest
```

Fix all failures before committing. This matches `.github/workflows/lint.yml` and `test.yml`.

For quick fixes: `poetry run ruff format .` and `poetry run ruff check --fix .`, then re-run the checks above.
